<p><strong>OSINT (open source intelligence) is the information you can find about someone from content that is openly available on the internet</strong>. Apart from the obvious content (name, DOB etcŌĆ”), using metadata from photos, analysis of photos, information on family etcŌĆ” can reveal far more!</p>

